re left]] Economic: [[Centre right]] to [[right wing]]\n|-\n{{Canadian party colour|CA|Marijuana|row}}\n| [[Marijuana Party (Canada)|Marijuana Party]]<br /><small>{{lang|fr|Parti Marijuana}}</small>\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 2000\n| [[Legality of cannabis|Cannabis legalisation]]\n| [[Blair Longley]]\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| [[Single issue]]\n|-\n{{Canadian party colour|CA|Marxist-Leninist|row}}\n| [[Communist Party of Canada (Marxist\u2013Leninist)|Marxist\u2013Leninist Party of Canada]]<br /><small>{{lang|fr|Parti Marxiste\u2013L\u00e9niniste du Canada}}</small>\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 1970\n| [[Anti-Revisionism|Anti-Revisionist Marxism-Leninism]]\n| Anna Di Carlo\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| [[Far left]]\n|-\n{{Canadian party colour|CA|National Citizens Alliance|row}}\n| [[National Citizens Alliance]]<br /><small>{{lang|fr|Alliance Nationale des Citoyens}}</small>\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 2014\n| [[Right-wing populism]], [[anti-globalism]], [[white nationalism]]\n| Stephen J. Garvey\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| [[Far right]]\n|-\n{{Canadian party colour|CA||row}}\n| ''Parti pour l'Ind\u00e9pendance du Qu\u00e9bec''\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 2019\n| [[Quebec nationalism]], [[Quebec sovereigntism]]\n| Michel Blondin\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0\n|\n|-\n{{Canadian party colour|CA|PPC|row}}\n| [[People's Party of Canada]]<br /><small>{{lang|fr|Parti populaire du Canada}}</small>\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 2018\n| [[Conservatism in Canada|Conservatism]], [[Right-wing populism]], [[Classical liberalism]], 